ing: 1 (8 ounce) container frozen whipped topping, thawed
des: "This is a favorite holiday treat for my family.  It can be made with sugar free  gelatin, fat free cottage cheese, and fat free cool whip for a lower calorie treat.  This is an EASY and quick treat!"
ins: In a mixing bowl, combine the gelatin mix, cottage cheese, whipped topping and pineapple. Mix together well, refrigerate until chilled and serve.
